This is a state mandated requirement.

Jazlynn plans to attend Central High School and says her favorite memory from Brushy is when the 7th/8th Grade Football team won the State Championship.
Jazlynn would like to leave you with these Words of Wisdom:
Good things come to those who believe, better things come to those who are patient, and the best things come to those who don't give up.
